    About

    Description

    Mohmad Zaid Sutar is currently pursuing a Bachelor of Technology in Artificial Intelligence and Data Science (3rd year). A dedicated and passionate individual, he has developed a strong foundation in AI through both academic and practical experiences. Zaid's accomplishments include qualifying for the state level of India Skills, reflecting his commitment to excellence in his field. With a keen interest in innovative technology, he is driven to contribute to impactful projects that advance the application of AI and data science. Linkedin
